        "intro-text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>What started as a shared dream between two chefs has grown into one of Brooklyn's most beloved dining destinations. At Saffron, every dish tells a story — of the farmer who grew the heirloom tomatoes, the fisherman who caught the morning's halibut, and the hands that shaped the pasta by hand.</p><p>We believe great food is about more than what's on the plate. It's about the people around the table, the conversations that linger, and the moments that become memories.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "intro-button": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "link": {
              "text": "About Us",
              "href": "about.html",
              "target": "_self"
            },
            "style": "secondary",
            "size": "medium",
            "position": "right"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["intro-eyebrow", "intro-heading", "intro-text", "intro-button"]
